OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FProsecute Taliban crimes   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagainst women - Brown      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban's treatment of women and   
OL,6, girls in Afghanistan is a "crime       
OL,7, against humanity", Gordon Brown has    
OL,8, told the BBC.                          
OL,10,FThe former prime minister is calling on
OL,11,Fthe International Criminal Court (ICC) 
OL,12,Fto prosecute those responsible for the 
OL,13,F"vicious" abuse of human rights.       
OL,15,FThe Taliban government has severely    
OL,16,Frestricted the freedoms of women and   
OL,17,Fgirls since regaining power in 2021.   
OL,19,F"This is the systematic brutalisation  
OL,20,Fof women and girls," he said.          
